6}$F suffered from\nthe low cross sections for the population of excited states in $^{25}$O because\nof low spectroscopic factors. In this respect, neutron transfer reactions carry\nmore promise.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 12 Oct 2017 20:20:31 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-11-29"}
